The paper deals with multi-agent systems and planning, which are core topics in the field of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses coordination and communication, which are important aspects of distributed computing (cs.DC). The proposed algorithms involve optimization and decision-making, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with dynamic environments, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO).
